data.description: *Photos Coming Soon* Tremendous Value! Great home in Great Location! Newer roof installed in 2020.  There is ample off-street parking for 4 vehicles located in vibrant, up and coming Mount Rainier, this home is just a few doors down from GLUT, a natural food co-op selling locally sourced produce and surrounded by local hotspots, like the award-winning restaurant Pennyroyal Station, Red Dirt, Studio, Vigilante Coffee and Era wine bar. Quick access to bike trails and public transportation, along with other nearby amenities including shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Just blocks from the D.C. line, commuting is a breeze with easy access to major highways, College Park and more. Call today to schedule a time to view this home!
